uld provide strong constraints on the water\nerosion around UCDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 May 2016 18:58:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2016 12:01:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
